Before Running this app :
1. change the gmail credentials in properties file.
2. Enable less secure functionality of gamil.

##################################################### 


1. For Submit a participant request

(POST) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation 

(BODY) : 

{
	"participantName" : "Brayan",
	"participantCountry" : "HK",
	"participantAge" : 25,
	"email" : "pankajkaalyan@gmail.com"
}

-------------------------------------------------

2. For getting all participations

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation

-------------------------------------------------

3. For getting a specific participations

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/{participantId}

example : localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/1617913901208
-------------------------------------------------

4. For creating groups of participants

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/groups/{numberOfParticipantsInSingleGroup}

example : localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/groups/4
-------------------------------------------------

5. For getting groups of participants

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/groups

-------------------------------------------------

6. For getting all first round matches of league.

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/matches

-------------------------------------------------

7. For getting all match results ..

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/results

-------------------------------------------------

8. For getting a specific match result ..

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/results/{matchId}

example: localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/result/c2fa11fc-e72d-4099-9215-fffbbe2c2a71

-------------------------------------------------

9. For getting a specific match result ..

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/results/{matchId}

example: localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/result/c2fa11fc-e72d-4099-9215-fffbbe2c2a71

-------------------------------------------------

10. For getting a winner of league ..
	Winner can be declared only when all matches of first round has been played.
	
	In this functionality, a mail will be sent to the winner's email Id.

(GET) localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/winner

example: localhost:8080/league/v1/participation/winner





 



